Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:18.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かり ません
